description: Kink.com designated a private, single-stall bathroom in the Armory as the dedicated place for models to douche and do enemas. In an effort to celebrate this happy occasion, the experienced and informative Ariel X volunteered to discuss and demonstrate for Behind Kink’s viewers the merits and methods of giving oneself an enema. So grab your notebook, pop a squat, and prepare to absorb a full dose of education on the mysteriously alluring practice of the enema.
title: Enema Basics with Ariel X
